  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 84736f00ca5690940aa2333ea4ce800b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dream3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - When Dad tried to move us with him to district 1, she fought back hard. I hadn't
    seen her so angry since her hero days.
  - I remember finding her after he left, she locked herself in her workshop. But
    I was good at getting in places I'm not supposed to.
  - Red-rimmed eyes, puffy from crying, staring at the wall. It was like she wasn't
    even there... It was the scariest moment of my life.
  - 'And the day I vowed to be her hero. '
  responses: []
